e="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; width: 728px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; vertical-align: bottom; margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important; max-width: none !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important;" title="3rd party ad content" name="google_ads_iframe_/93581981/Hipwee_Desktop_NonStandard_0" width="1" height="1" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no" data-google-container-id="8" data-load-complete="true"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Berkunjung ke danau Toba di Sumatera mungkin dulu tidak terlalu populer seperti Bali atau Lombok. Namun beberapa tahun belakangan danau Toba jadi lebih terkenal karena merupakan destinasi wisata andalan pemerintah. Berkunjung ke sana dengan kekasih merupakan pilihan yang menarik di tahun ini.</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 19px; font-size: 17px;">2. Pulau Labengki yang sering disebut mini Raja Ampat ini punya Teluk Cinta yang lovable banget lho</h3>\r\n<div id="attachment_532863" class="wp-caption aligncenter fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img class="size-large wp-image-532863 fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; max-height: 340px;" src="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-Teluk-Cinta-Pulau-Labengki-Sulawesi-Tenggara-750x421.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" srcset="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-Teluk-Cinta-Pulau-Labengki-Sulawesi-Tenggara-750x422.jpg 750w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-Teluk-Cinta-Pulau-Labengki-Sulawesi-Tenggara-640x359.jpg 640w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-Teluk-Cinta-Pulau-Labengki-Sulawesi-Tenggara-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-Teluk-Cinta-Pulau-Labengki-Sulawesi-Tenggara-360x203.jpg 360w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-Teluk-Cinta-Pulau-Labengki-Sulawesi-Tenggara.jpg 800w" alt="" width="750" height="421" />\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3px 0px 10px; color: #8e8e8e; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.857; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.026px;">teluk cinta pulau labengki via&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; border-bottom: 2px solid #f8af5b;" href="http://bugistraveler.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Teluk-Cinta-Pulau-Labengki-Sulawesi-Tenggara.jpg" target="new">bugistraveler.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Pulau Labengki terletak di Provinsi Sulawesi Tenggara. Pulau ini bersama Sombori sering disebut sebagai mini Raja Ampat karena bentuk bukit-bukit karangnya yang mirip dengan Raja Ampat. Jangan sampai kelupaan mengunjungi Teluk Cinta ya kalau berlibur ke sana.</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 19px; font-size: 17px;">3. Dieng Culture Festival selalu jadi momen romantis bagi ribuan pengunjung yang hadir ke sana. Tahun ini pun masih sama romantisnya!</h3>\r\n<div id="attachment_444465" class="wp-caption aligncenter fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img class="size-large wp-image-444465 fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; max-height: 340px;" src="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hipwee-1489839921191-750x637.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" srcset="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hipwee-1489839921191-750x637.jpg 750w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hipwee-1489839921191-640x544.jpg 640w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hipwee-1489839921191-768x652.jpg 768w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hipwee-1489839921191-250x212.jpg 250w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hipwee-1489839921191.jpg 1361w" alt="" width="750" height="637" />\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3px 0px 10px; color: #8e8e8e; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.857; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.026px;">dieng festival via&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; border-bottom: 2px solid #f8af5b;" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/BRyAGYGFout/?taken-by=sociotraveler" target="new">www.instagram.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Setiap tahunnya, Dieng Culture Festival selalu jadi festival yang paling disukai pasangan muda. Betapa tidak, festival Jazz dengan suasana dingin disertai pelepasan lampion jadi sebuah moment romantis yang nggak bakal terlupakan. Datang ya ke Dieng bulan Agustus nanti!</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 19px; font-size: 17px;">4. Nusa Penida kini jadi primadona baru di Bali. Alam yang masih perawan dan alami bikin perjalananmu dengan pasangan bakalan tak terlupakan!</h3>\r\n<div id="attachment_576798" class="wp-caption aligncenter fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img class="size-large wp-image-576798 fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; max-height: 340px;" src="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/hipwee-22277535_124192281665266_8487577335128653824_n-750x500.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" srcset="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/hipwee-22277535_124192281665266_8487577335128653824_n-750x500.jpg 750w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/hipwee-22277535_124192281665266_8487577335128653824_n-640x427.jpg 640w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/hipwee-22277535_124192281665266_8487577335128653824_n-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/hipwee-22277535_124192281665266_8487577335128653824_n.jpg 1080w" alt="" width="750" height="500" />\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3px 0px 10px; color: #8e8e8e; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.857; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.026px;">crystal bay, nusa penida via&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; border-bottom: 2px solid #f8af5b;" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/BZ8lhCjFOld/?taken-by=ayanggkahiyang" target="new">www.instagram.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Nusa Penida dalam beberapa tahun terakhir jadi alternatif wisata utama di Bali. Lokasinya yang terpisah pulau dengan Bali membuat pulau ini masih terjaga dan masih tampak sangat alami. Datanah ke Kelingking beach, Atuh beach, Angel&rsquo;s Billabong dan destinasi menarik lainnya di sana.</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 19px; font-size: 17px;">5. Belitung punya pantai-pantai berbatu yang spektakuler dan instagenic. Kamu dan kekasih bakalan betah menikmati indahnya pulau Laskar Pelangi ini</h3>\r\n<div id="attachment_49736" class="wp-caption aligncenter fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img class="size-large wp-image-49736 fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; max-height: 340px;" src="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/tanjung-tinggi-belitung-750x500.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" srcset="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/tanjung-tinggi-belitung-750x500.jpg 750w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/tanjung-tinggi-belitung-640x427.jpg 640w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/tanjung-tinggi-belitung-360x240.jpg 360w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/tanjung-tinggi-belitung.jpg 933w" alt="" width="750" height="500" />\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3px 0px 10px; color: #8e8e8e; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.857; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.026px;">Keindahan di Pantai Laskar Pelangi, Tanjung Tinggi. via&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; border-bottom: 2px solid #f8af5b;" href="http://www.indonesia.travel/id%29/destination/631/belitung-the-island-beyond-the-rainbow" target="new">www.indonesia.travel</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Belitung punya pantai-pantai yang indah dan berbatu. Batu-batu granit berukuran raksasa di tepian pantai-pantai Belitung sungguh unik dan mengagumkan. Cocok sekali untuk bulan madu bersama kekasihmu tercinta.</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 19px; font-size: 17px;">6. Sumba adalah destinasi wisata yang sedang hits 2-3 tahun terakhir. Nggak cuma instagramable, Sumba juga begitu romantis</h3>\r\n<div id="attachment_795168" class="wp-caption aligncenter fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img class="size-large wp-image-795168 fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; max-height: 340px;" src="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-main_image_17954-750x493.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" srcset="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-main_image_17954-750x493.jpg 750w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-main_image_17954-640x421.jpg 640w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-main_image_17954-768x505.jpg 768w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-main_image_17954-250x164.jpg 250w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-main_image_17954.jpg 800w" alt="" width="750" height="493" />\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3px 0px 10px; color: #8e8e8e; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.857; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.026px;">sumba via&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; border-bottom: 2px solid #f8af5b;" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/Bbjl9GVB4lM/" target="new">www.instagram.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Destinasi idaman para selebgram, Sumba, memang wajib kamu datangi di tahun ini. Hamparan savana ala Afrika dan deretan pantai-pantai indahnya bakal bikin betah bermesraan dengan pasangan tercinta. Apalagi destinasi wisata di Sumba itu sangatlah fotogenic dan instagramable.</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 19px; font-size: 17px;">7. Labuan Bajo nggak pernah bikin kita kecewa. Meski Gili Lawa terbakar, namun pesonanya tidak pernah pudar</h3>\r\n<div id="attachment_521893" class="wp-caption aligncenter fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img class="size-large wp-image-521893 fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; max-height: 340px;" src="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-download-2-750x500.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" srcset="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-download-2-750x500.jpg 750w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-download-2-640x427.jpg 640w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-download-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-download-2-250x167.jpg 250w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hipwee-download-2.jpg 1000w" alt="" width="750" height="500" />\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3px 0px 10px; color: #8e8e8e; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.857; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.026px;">padar island via&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; border-bottom: 2px solid #f8af5b;" href="http://www.escapejournal.co/allposts/2016/10/15/padar-island-the-most-beautiful-island-in-komodo-national-park" target="new">www.escapejournal.co</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Romantisme mana lagi yang bisa mengalahkan sailing trip dengan kapal di kepulauan Komodo termasuk ke Padar, Kelor, Pantai Pink hingga Pulau Rinca? Labuan Bajo terlalu indah bagi kamu yang sedang memadu cinta. Uhuy~</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 19px; font-size: 17px;">8. Bukit Merese Lombok punya pemandangan yang romantis sekaligus menakjubkan. Datanglah saat senja tiba dan rasakan syahdunya</h3>\r\n<div id="attachment_795030" class="wp-caption aligncenter fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img class="size-large wp-image-795030 fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; max-height: 340px;" src="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-a754e35b36792127ba51ff0d88ae7925-750x500.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" srcset="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-a754e35b36792127ba51ff0d88ae7925-750x500.jpg 750w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-a754e35b36792127ba51ff0d88ae7925-640x427.jpg 640w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-a754e35b36792127ba51ff0d88ae7925-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-a754e35b36792127ba51ff0d88ae7925-250x167.jpg 250w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-a754e35b36792127ba51ff0d88ae7925.jpg 1080w" alt="" width="750" height="500" />\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3px 0px 10px; color: #8e8e8e; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.857; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.026px;">bukit merese via&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; border-bottom: 2px solid #f8af5b;" href="https://www.instagram.com/nadinelist" target="new">www.instagram.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Meski belum lama ini dihantam gempa besar, Lombok tetaplah Lombok. Sebuah pulau yang menyajikan keindahan alam paripurna. Cobalah datang ke Bukit Merese saat senja tiba dan rasakan syahdunya bersama kekasihmu di atas bukit hijau sana.</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 19px; font-size: 17px;">9. Danau Love di Jayapura punya nama asli danau Imfote yang berada tak jauh dari Danau Sentani. Bentuknya aja kaya hatiku ke kamu. Eaaa~</h3>\r\n<div id="attachment_792554" class="wp-caption aligncenter fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img class="size-large wp-image-792554 fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; max-height: 340px;" src="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-40522938_1954137524886791_5330301106466342096_n-750x572.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" srcset="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-40522938_1954137524886791_5330301106466342096_n-750x572.jpg 750w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-40522938_1954137524886791_5330301106466342096_n-640x488.jpg 640w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-40522938_1954137524886791_5330301106466342096_n-768x586.jpg 768w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-40522938_1954137524886791_5330301106466342096_n-250x191.jpg 250w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hipwee-40522938_1954137524886791_5330301106466342096_n.jpg 1080w" alt="" width="750" height="572" />\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3px 0px 10px; color: #8e8e8e; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.857; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.026px;">danau imfote via&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; border-bottom: 2px solid #f8af5b;" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/Bnh9EhFg0L-/" target="new">www.instagram.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Kalau ke Papua nggak sah dong kalau nggak berkunjung ke Danau Sentani tak jauh dari Jayapura. Ternyata nggak cuma ada Danau Sentani lho, ada juga Danau Love atau Imfote. Bentuk &lsquo;love&rsquo; danaunya ini instagramable banget sih. Sekarang banyak nih selebgram yang berfoto di sana.</p>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 19px; font-size: 17px;">10. Jogja selalu lekat dengan kenangan yang tak kunjung hilang. Apalagi kalau berburu senja di tebing paralayang di Parangendog dengan pemandangan laut selatan</h3>\r\n<div id="attachment_783132" class="wp-caption aligncenter fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 15px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img class="size-large wp-image-783132 fade-in" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; max-height: 340px;" src="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/hipwee-44921522_120337728972466_1453748691144229459_n-750x938.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" srcset="https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/hipwee-44921522_120337728972466_1453748691144229459_n-750x938.jpg 750w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/hipwee-44921522_120337728972466_1453748691144229459_n-640x800.jpg 640w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/hipwee-44921522_120337728972466_1453748691144229459_n-768x960.jpg 768w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/hipwee-44921522_120337728972466_1453748691144229459_n-200x250.jpg 200w, https://cdn-asset.hipwee.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/hipwee-44921522_120337728972466_1453748691144229459_n.jpg 1080w" alt="" width="750" height="938" />\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 3px 0px 10px; color: #8e8e8e; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.857; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.026px;">parangendog via&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; border-bottom: 2px solid #f8af5b;" href="https://www.instagram.com/taufiqurhman_/" target="new">www.instagram.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Ada satu spot berburu senja di Jogja yang harus kamu coba, yakni Bukit Paralayang di Parangendog. Lokasinya sekitar 20 menit perjalanan dari pantai Parangtritis ke arah Gunungkidul. Kini spot ini sudah dibangun untuk wisatawan yang mau hunting sunset. Kalau sama pasangan romantis juga nih. Malamnya bisa jajan di Sate Klathak Pak Pong. Nikmat mana yang kamu dustakan?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Lalu, tahun 2019 ini mau ajak pasangan kamu ke mana? Jomblo nggak usah baper ya. Ajakin temen-temen aja deh kalau nggak ada pasangan. Hehehe.</p>', '2019-01-10 12:16:25', '2019-01-10 12:16:25', NULL);
